{"abstract": "Group travel and social events are taking a bigger share of M.B.A. students\u2019 time \u2014 and money.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/05/18/business/in-b-school-is-that-a-syllabus-or-an-itinerary.html", "snippet": "Group travel and social events are taking a bigger share of M.B.A. students\u2019 time \u2014 and money.", "lead_paragraph": "One weekend in February, about a third of Sean Pool\u2019s classmates at the McCombs School of Business at the University of Texas at Austin went on a three-day ski trip to Park City, Utah. The event included nighttime, apr\u00e8s-ski outings in town, as well as time to relax in a hot tub, according to the itinerary posted on Facebook. The Graduate Business Adventure Team, a student-run group, planned the trip. ", "print_section": "BU", "print_page": "6", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/05/18/business/18-BSCHOOL-1/18-BSCHOOL-1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 407, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/05/18/business/18-BSCHOOL-1/18-BSCHOOL-1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 407}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/05/18/business/18-BSCHOOL-1/18-BSCHOOL-1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 695, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/05/18/business/18-BSCHOOL-1/18-BSCHOOL-1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1391, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/05/18/business/18-BSCHOOL-1/18-BSCHOOL-1-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbSta